<div class="jsx-355086517 desc">The finest in luxury living in the heart of prestigious Buckhead. Modern-styled home with classic architectural elements designed by acclaimed architect Yong Pak. The home is featured in several design magazines and encompasses 8.692 sq. ft. nestled on .98 acres of land. There are 7 bedrooms, 7 full baths, and 2 half baths. A gourmet kitchen, library, gymnasium, and a 3-car garage. The home incorporates the finest exotic finishes from around the world and offers outdoor space for children, including their very own treehouse. Bluestone decking, veranda, and sun porch. Custom finished wide-plank flooring with 10-foot ceilings and 9-foot solid core doors with European bronzed hardware. Custom ebonized European windows and doors spanning the entire rear of the home. Antique French wood and iron double entry door. Hand painted ceiling in master bedroom and multiple fireplaces with imported marbles and granites. Chinese Toile on guest bedroom walls. Heated floors in all bathrooms, and steam shower in master bath. Whole home, gas powered back-up generator. All steel construction and beautiful slate roof. Adjacent lot with just over an acre of land for additional privacy available under separate negotiation. Luxury and convenience at its best.</div>
